Punish griefers or mess with your friends!

Spawn certain numbers of mobs and other entities at a certain player's position, or where you are looking.

Commands and Permissions
<required>, [optional]
/creep [player] [#] - spawn a creeper[s] at the player's position, or where you are looking
/enderman [player] [#] - spawn an enderman [or more than one] at the player's position, or where you are looking
/skeleton [player] [#] - spawn a skeleton [or more than one] at the player's position, or where you are looking
/spider [player] [#] - spawn a skeleton [or more than one] at the player's position, or where you are looking